  "prompt": "Do they have wifi at Kirorimal College Hostel?",
  "response": "As of my knowledge cutoff in October 2023, Kirorimal College Hostel in Delhi generally provides Wi-Fi facilities to its residents to support academic and personal needs. However, the quality and availability of the internet connection can vary based on factors such as the number of users and maintenance schedules.\n\nFor the most accurate and up-to-date information, I recommend reaching out directly to Kirorimal College's administration or the hostel management. They can provide specific details about the current Wi-Fi services, including any recent upgrades or changes to the connectivity infrastructure.\n\n**Contact Information:**\n\n- **Kirorimal College, Delhi University**\n- **Address:** Kamla Nehru Marg, Delhi University, New Delhi, Delhi 110067, India\n- **Phone:** You can find the most recent contact numbers on the [official Kirorimal College website](http://www.kscmission.org/)\n- **Email:** Typically, colleges have specific email addresses for hostel inquiries, which can also be found on their official website.\n\nReaching out directly will ensure you receive the most reliable and updated information regarding Wi-Fi and other hostel amenities.",
